{"tid":355060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨林子健被中國打  跟住釋放  擺到明係扮嘢","createTime":"2017-08-11T03:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T11:45:08.000Z","uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c332184cff08ec672886e06da4095955fe9311","tid":355060,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係中國扮嘢，得個嚇字</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係呀，係痛呀<br />\n<br />\n畀人打，畀釘書機釘係好痛呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又如何？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">你要記住，佢點打你，你都仲係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人</span>。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢點打你，你都唔會變成<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國人</span>。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">香港人嘅自豪，香港人嘅優越，可以咁容易就畀<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國人</span></span>打幾下就冇咗架咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中國會敢打香港人打到我哋死咩？<br />\n<br />\n佢夠膽咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國連印度都驚呀大佬！</span><br />\n<br />\n就算真係有香港人被中國殺死，只會令到<span style=\"color: maroon;\">社會撕裂一發不可收拾</span>。<br />\n<br />\n佢夠膽咩？<br />\n<br />\n中國人有膽嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">區區皮肉痛楚，香港人有咩怕過？</span></span>"},{"pid":"972e0ea1a933435cb5bac50b249e75ebd20beb25","tid":355060,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T03:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de251bcbba10f87af986a6c1fa446a1bdfff662f","tid":355060,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2